{"tid":2267364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私人檢控遭干預 泛民原告變被告  建制派連環施襲 警方、律政司包庇","createTime":"2020-11-02T04:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T05:57:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2669b35ea8cfde43b6da636e8916e7cee7ddbf","tid":2267364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/2HKVJ7DXUREBLE5IWWYCUE5T5I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F2HKVJ7DXUREBLE5IWWYCUE5T5I%2F&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=bc994588\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201102%2F2HKVJ7DXUREBLE5IWWYCUE5T5I%2F&h=b60be9e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201102/2HKVJ7DXUREBLE5IWWYCUE5T5I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n私人檢控遭干預 泛民原告變被告 <br />\n建制派連環施襲 警方、律政司包庇<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】七名民主派人士昨因涉5.8立會內會衝突被捕，當日多名建制派議員均有參與衝突，工聯會郭偉强更涉打傷陳志全，惟陳報案後警方無執法，要陳自行向郭提私人檢控；當日民建聯黃定光、周浩鼎亦疑似向多人「批㬹」，何君堯更一度擺出打拳狀挑釁，但他們統統沒被捕。民主派怒斥警方及律政司以雙重標準及選擇性執法打壓異己，陳志全更指律政司正考慮介入其私人檢控，質疑想放生郭偉强，令他們由原告變被告。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：西環集中營：港府大龍鳳或觸發泛民總辭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5jtGwKyBHtC8ZUpub12k5u7CYpk=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FQDDG2DC3BBFNBRLAHNXD74Z7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5jtGwKyBHtC8ZUpub12k5u7CYpk%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFQDDG2DC3BBFNBRLAHNXD74Z7M.jpg&h=4428eef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳志全在5月8日立會衝突時，遭郭偉强粗暴拖行，惟警方對此猶如視若無睹。<br />\n<br />\n翻查當天內會情況，由於未獲授權選出的民建聯李慧琼強行坐上主席位主持內會，民主派與建制派議員湧至台前互相指罵，。。。。。。。。。。。另一建制派議員何君堯除跟民主派議員對罵，更一度擺出打拳姿勢挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n當日有份參與衝突建制派議員，沒任何人被捕，陳志全5月11日到灣仔警總就遭郭偉强事件報案，並同步提私人檢控，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：未收被捕通知 許智峯：放馬過來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NgoltWJIO4HohM7UgIwi920SC2U=/1316x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UQOPI5ORFNEWZA5MCOK4N4NWQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNgoltWJIO4HohM7UgIwi920SC2U%3D%2F1316x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUQOPI5ORFNEWZA5MCOK4N4NWQY.jpg&h=fe2d3b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何君堯當日擺出打拳姿勢，企圖挑釁泛民議員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WKAeroezrzi0-GZe0tttFGW6PkM=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5JKF53YAVNDRBPJYNLU4NVZ444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWKAeroezrzi0-GZe0tttFGW6PkM%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5JKF53YAVNDRBPJYNLU4NVZ444.jpg&h=b6a1dfc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方昨開記招交代拘捕民主派事宜，惟避答會否拉郭偉强。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳志全轟港府顛倒是非<br />\n<br />\n陳志全昨獲釋後指，極權政府以警隊、律政司和法庭打壓異己，「當日好清楚郭偉强襲擊我，半年過去，警察同律政司乜都冇做過，今日卻拘捕一班民主派立法會議員，可見特區政府如何顛倒是非黑白」。對於律政司介入私人檢控，他直言最差結果非撤銷對郭檢控，「係原告變被告」，形容事件不公平，是政治選擇性拘捕和檢控，以及選擇性不檢控不拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n至於當日另一原告及傷者尹兆堅，警方刑事偵緝隊當晚已跟他錄口供。他。。。。。。。。。。。，點解矛頭只針對民主派？」認為警方應亦檢控建制派。<br />\n<br />\n當日的「內會主席」李慧琼指議會情況混亂，她運用主席權力把議員逐離場。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o-VXoy97c4LdihzjV3h4QpHyVRk=/554x1220/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q5A2IT4IIFCMLGKDM76LFSJFZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo-VXoy97c4LdihzjV3h4QpHyVRk%3D%2F554x1220%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ5A2IT4IIFCMLGKDM76LFSJFZQ.png&h=b7435a81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7859bd7b7b81fd3961e2bf03e8078a0a9830204","tid":2267364,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"坐監有冇10萬糧出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n儍閪小丑"}]}